item.title: Need help with galkons anarchy v1.5!
item.dc:creator: @agent_nukks agent nukks
item.description:
@agent_nukks wrote:

Well if your trying to connect to your server, your going to have to go in client.java, and search for his ip name, so if the ip your connecting to on the client is “galkon.no-ip.org” Look that up, doing CTRL + H, then replacing the names. To change the overall IP go into a file named “EGUI” and there should eb three quotants with an IP in them, change those to your servers ip, goodluck.
